ix well. Spread a quarter of the couscous mixture loosely on Varoma dish, leaving some holes unobstructed so steam can circulate, and spread remaining couscous on Varoma tray. Place 400 g water in mixing bowl and insert simmering basket with vegetables. Set Varoma in position and steam <b>17 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Transfer couscous to a large serving dish and gently fluff the couscous using a fork. Drizzle steamed vegetables with 1 tbsp olive oil and stir gently to coat. Remove simmering basket using spatula and arrange vegetables around the couscous. Serve hot, garnished with chopped parsley and reserved feta cheese."}],"basicInfo":["medium","45m","1h 15m","6 portions"]}